Package TimeOfDay

Class TimeOfDay

java.lang.Object
TimeOfDay.TimeOfDay
public class TimeOfDay
extends java.lang.Object
Each instance represents the time of the day as two separate integers: hours and minutes.
Immutable
Any two calls of any zero-argument getter of this class on the same target object return equal values. (A getter is a method whose name starts with "get" or "is" followed by a capital letter.)
Invariants:
The hours integer cannot exceed 24. 
getHours() <= 24
The hours must be non-negative. 
getHours() >= 0
The minutes integer cannot exceed 60. 
getMinutes() <= 60
minutes must be non-negative. 
getMinutes() >= 0
